quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,10,"In their hearts is disease, so Allāh has increased their disease;{1} and for them is a painful punishment because they [habitually] used to lie.",footnotes:1:[The "disease" mentioned here includes doubt, hypocrisy, arrogance and disbelief.]
  2,11,"And when it is said to them, "
  2,12,"Unquestionably, it is they who are the corrupters, but they perceive [it] not."